snippet.title: FaeTerra - Pre-alpha gameplay!
snippet.description:
Auto-Battler combining management, deckbuilding, and 121 adorable creatures.​
Pre-Alpha gameplay footage of my indie game FaeTerra!

Visit our website: https://www.solfiregames.com/
Join the community: https://discord.gg/solfiregames

Coming soon to PC IOS and Android.
